        <APITestDescription>
            <TestedClass name="java.lang.ClassLoader"/>
            <TestedMethod name="protected Class&lt;?&gt; loadClass(String name, boolean resolve) throws ClassNotFoundException"/>
            <Description>
The test is against the loadClass1011 method.

The test performs the following checks on the method.
1) ClassNotFoundException is thrown if a class with specified name cannot be found.
2) ClassNotFoundException is not thrown if 
   a class with specified name can be found and "boolean resolve" is false.
3) ClassNotFoundException is not thrown if 
   a class with specified name can be found and "boolean resolve" is true.
            </Description>
